  51. ‌type alloc_dbginfo_item =
  52.   { alloc_words : int;
  53.     alloc_dbg : t }
  54. (** Due to Comballoc, a single Ialloc instruction may combine several
  55.     unrelated allocations. Their Debuginfo.t (which may differ) are stored
  56.     as a list of alloc_dbginfo. This list is in order of increasing memory
  57.     address, which is the reverse of the original allocation order. Later
  58.     allocations are consed to the front of this list by Comballoc. *)

  60. ‌type alloc_dbginfo = alloc_dbginfo_item list
